Reclusa::

Reclusa smiled evilly. "I am decended from Black Arachnia. I have
webbing, lazar blasters, and when needed, exposives. I am a capable
fighter, and enjoy consumming the fluids from my prey. I am skilled in
many weapons and tactical use of them.  I also am highly skilled at
recon."  She paused a moment to let him think on what she said. "My
venom is not only with my fangs but my tongue as well. I am skilled at
translating codes and finding hidden signals. I do have many
leadership programs at my disposal and know how to use them
effectively."  She gave him a modest smile, still holding herself
high. "I trust that I have skills you will find useful." 

She felt like an advertisement holoboard from Cybertron at that point.
Last thing she wanted to do was try to sell herself.  She had expected
him to just accept her and not feel that he needed to test her.
However, perhaps her releasing information of some of her capabilities
would give her an instant rank possition, and not just something from
the bottom of the ranks.
